, intending to trade the bishop on h5 after Bg2-f3. For instance,} Ke7 17. Bf3
Rhg8 18. Kd2 Nf6 19. Nf4 $14 {Black is doomed to passive defence.}) 16. Rg3 $5
$146 {I find this new idea rather logical: the Rg3 puts more pressure on f5.} (
