({After} 16... a5 17. Rf3 $1 a4 18. Ng3 Rhg8 19. Bh3 $14 {, the f5-pawn will
fall soon and Black still doesn't have any counterplay.}) ({Also after} 16...
Rhg8 17. Bh3 Ne4 18. Rf3 Nd6 19. Ng3 {, Black struggles to maintain the
material balance.}) 17. Rf3 Rhg8 ({The attempt to activate the forces with} 
