Black's rook+pawn.}) 18. Bh3 Ng7 19. Ng3 a5 20. Kd2 $14 {White can slowly
improve his position and choose a moment to capture on f5. Of course, Black
still has decent chances to hold this endgame, but it is far from enjoyable.} *

