tempi to activate most of his pieces.} Qd6 16. d5 {A well-timed break. Black
is forced to move the knight back.} exd5 17. exd5 Nb8 18. O-O {Black struggles
to complete his development as} Nd7 {runs into} 19. Qd4 Bf6 20. Bb4 {, with
